PIM is dependent on MySQL. 

Instruction on howto install, configure and create the database with the proper
permissions you can find in the MySQL manual.

To import the database structure you can use the command:

$ mysql -u pim -p pim < db-structure.sql

To configure the database connection for PIM change the variables appropriatly
and add its contents to pim.conf in the root of the PIM project.

[database]
host = "localhost"
username = "pim"
password = "pim"
database = "pim"
